name: Koi Sizzle #012 (1/1)
description: "Koi Sizzle" is the first project created by the artist collective, "NFT Sizzle". The RGB color of the Koi, the background, the spots on the Koi, and the three different alternating background elements were all chosen by a random number generator, then the pictures were assembled by hand. Only 100 will ever be minted and no 2 will be the same. The sale price of each original "Koi Sizzle" will increase with each purchase.
